Package Model

Class Space

java.lang.Object
Model.Space
All Implemented Interfaces:
BoardConfig
public class Space
extends java.lang.Object
implements BoardConfig
Space is the class that contains the attributes and methods to implement the behavior of a space in the Thats Life! game.
